OL,3,C'Risk of school closures' over
OL,4,Cdeterioration and #800m maintenance
OL,5,Cbacklog
OL,7,FThe Education Authority (EA) has
OL,8,Fwarned a lack of funding for school
OL,9,Frepairs could lead to more classrooms
OL,10,Fbeing closed on safety grounds.
OL,12,FThe EA suggested the maintenance
OL,13,Fbacklog could now stand up to #800
OL,14,Fmillion.
OL,16,FThe body is responsible for an
OL,17,Fextensive public estate across
OL,18,FNorthern Ireland, involving more than
OL,19,Fa 1,100 schools, worth an estimated
OL,20,Fvalue of #4.6 billion.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/7
