FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1781768876
OL,3,C'Risk of school closures' over
OL,4,Cdeterioration and #800m maintenance
OL,5,Cbacklog
OL,7,FA critical report from the Stormont
OL,8,FPublic Accounts Committee (PAC) last
OL,9,FOctober found that many schools are in
OL,10,Fa state of disrepair, describing the
OL,11,Fsituation as "unsafe" with an #800
OL,12,Fmillion bill for outstanding repairs
OL,13,Fand maintenance.
OL,15,FOn Wednesday, the EA warned that, if
OL,16,Fnot addressed, the position could soon
OL,17,Fbe reached where "schools, or part of
OL,18,Fschools, routinely need to close due
OL,19,Fto unaddressed maintenance issues".
OL,26,@sD@NOUsD@UO]yD@ROU{D@bO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/7
