OL,3,C'Risk of school closures' over
OL,4,Cdeterioration and #800m maintenance
OL,5,Cbacklog
OL,7,FEducation Minister Paul Givan has
OL,8,Fspoken about his department, which
OL,9,Ffunds the EA, facing a "severe funding
OL,10,Fcrisis".
OL,12,FOn Wednesday the EA said industry
OL,13,Fstandards suggest some #92 million is
OL,14,Fthe annual minimum spend to maintain
OL,15,Fits school estate.
OL,17,FBut in 2025/26 its maintenance budget
OL,18,Fprovided for total maintenance spend
OL,19,Fwas #61.1 million.
OL,26,@qD@XOUrD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
