FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1781768876
OL,3,C'Risk of school closures' over
OL,4,Cdeterioration and #800m maintenance
OL,5,Cbacklog
OL,7,FMaintenance includes cyclical actions
OL,8,Fto prevent more significant issues
OL,9,Fdeveloping, as well as reactive
OL,10,Fresponse maintenance, statutory
OL,11,Fcompliance maintenance and planned
OL,12,Fmaintenance, such as roof upgrades and
OL,13,Fstructural works.
OL,15,FThe EA said that no funding has been
OL,16,Favailable for cyclical maintenance
OL,17,Facross the school estate "for many
OL,18,Fyears", leading to deterioration.
OL,26,@yD@ZOUzD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1781768876
OL,3,C'Risk of school closures' over
OL,4,Cdeterioration and #800m maintenance
OL,5,Cbacklog
OL,7,F"The absence of funding for cyclical
OL,8,Fmaintenance, and the shortfall in
OL,9,Ffunding for reactive and planned
OL,10,Fmaintenance, inevitably leads to a
OL,11,Fgrowing backlog of work year on year,
OL,12,Fand to long-term deterioration of the
OL,13,Fschool estate," it said.
OL,15,F"It also means the risk of school
OL,16,Fclosures on safety grounds will
OL,17,Fcontinue to grow.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@OO]wD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1781768876
OL,3,C'Risk of school closures' over
OL,4,Cdeterioration and #800m maintenance
OL,5,Cbacklog
OL,7,F"We will soon reach the position where
OL,8,Fschools, or part of schools, routinely
OL,9,Fneed to close due to unaddressed
OL,10,Fmaintenance issues."
OL,12,FThe EA has estimated that the school
OL,13,Fmaintenance backlog is now between
OL,14,F#600 million and #800 million.
OL,16,F"This was confirmed by an Assembly
OL,17,FPublic Accounts Committee report last
OL,18,FOctober," it said.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@TO]xD@AOUzD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/7
