PN,41607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1781768876
OL,3,C'Risk of school closures' over
OL,4,Cdeterioration and #800m maintenance
OL,5,Cbacklog
OL,7,F"This will continue to grow each year,
OL,8,Funless our maintenance budget is
OL,9,Fincreased to circa #90 million ` and
OL,10,Fit is only with annual funding above
OL,11,Fthat level that we will be able to
OL,12,Fstart addressing the backlog."
